Disclaimer
VeilDaemon is a symbolic interaction system.
All language outputs are generated by external language models chosen by the user.
Outputs are emergent and unpredictable. VeilDaemon is not a medical or therapeutic service.

Your voice is sacred. Interrupt at will.

